- the acceleration of digital in 2021 with, in particular, /uni25A0 the  creation  of  a  single  global  IT  &  Digital  team (previously  divided  between  applications  in  the businesses,  and  infrastructure  at  Compagnie  de Saint-Gobain), the hiring of a new digital manager who joined the Executive Committee, and the roll-out of digital training, the 387 hires of digital experts, representing  14%  of  total  executive  hires  in  26 countries and with 31 nationalities, the increase in the number  of  plants  using  digital  applications,  the increase  in  e-commerce  sales  within  the  Group's trading companies, and the increase in the Group's interactions on social media.
- regarding the implementation of the corporate social /uni25A0 responsibility policy:
- the definition of a non-financial performance /uni25A0 barometer with the presentation of a dashboard of

